00:56:55,905 --> 00:56:57,371
Well...

826
00:56:57,406 --> 00:56:59,909
you kids
have a nice time.

827
00:56:59,944 --> 00:57:01,911
I'm going to see Abby.

828
00:57:06,916 --> 00:57:09,418
Your sister will
be here shortly.

829
00:57:31,941 --> 00:57:34,944
You can sit down
if you like.

830
00:57:37,947 --> 00:57:38,948
Sure.

831
00:58:08,477 --> 00:58:09,979
What's the matter
with you?

832
00:58:10,980 --> 00:58:12,982
Nothing's the matter.

833
00:58:13,017 --> 00:58:14,984
I'm letting you kiss me.

834
00:58:19,488 --> 00:58:21,991
Weren't you supposed
to let me try first?

835
00:58:36,505 --> 00:58:38,007
Hi there.

836
00:58:38,042 --> 00:58:40,592
Hi.

837
00:58:49,518 --> 00:58:52,021
Let me help you
with those things.

838
00:58:53,522 --> 00:58:56,025
Thank you.
I'd appreciate that.

839
00:59:00,529 --> 00:59:02,031
You must be Court.

840
00:59:05,034 --> 00:59:06,535
I've been
meaning to come by

841
00:59:07,036 --> 00:59:09,788
to visit with your mother
and say hi.

842
00:59:09,823 --> 00:59:12,541
I've been busy
getting ready for school

843
00:59:12,576 --> 00:59:15,044
that I didn't
get around to it.

844
00:59:15,079 --> 00:59:16,563
I promise I'll do it.

845
00:59:16,598 --> 00:59:18,047
Tell your mother that?

846
00:59:18,547 --> 00:59:21,050
Sure. She'll be
glad to see you.

847
00:59:21,550 --> 00:59:22,051
Thanks.

848
00:59:22,551 --> 00:59:23,552
Any time.

849
00:59:27,056 --> 00:59:28,891
You can
set these things down,

850
00:59:28,926 --> 00:59:31,060
and I can put them up.

851
00:59:31,560 --> 00:59:32,561
You must be Maureen.

852
00:59:33,062 --> 00:59:34,930
I forgot to say that,
didn't I?

853
00:59:37,432 --> 00:59:40,936
You two can go back to
whatever you were doing.

854
00:59:40,971 --> 00:59:42,402
I can handle this.

855
00:59:42,437 --> 00:59:44,371
Court, you want
to go walking?

856
00:59:44,406 --> 00:59:47,409
Why don't you two
do that, and, uh...

857
00:59:47,444 --> 00:59:49,195
I'll have
dinner ready

858
00:59:49,230 --> 00:59:50,911
by the time
you get back.

859
00:59:50,946 --> 00:59:51,947
You're welcome
to stay for supper

860
00:59:51,982 --> 00:59:52,948
if you'd like.

861
00:59:53,448 --> 00:59:54,449
Isn't he, Dani?

862
00:59:54,484 --> 00:59:55,467
Sure.

863
00:59:55,502 --> 00:59:56,416
Great.

864
00:59:56,451 --> 00:59:58,453
That's fine.
I'll set the table.

865
00:59:58,488 --> 01:00:00,455
Show me where
the things are.

866
01:00:00,622 --> 01:00:02,958
I think we ought
to have supper

867
01:00:02,993 --> 01:00:04,226
in the dining room,

868
01:00:04,261 --> 01:00:05,460
don't you, Dani?

869
01:00:05,495 --> 01:00:06,461
Whatever.

870
01:00:15,470 --> 01:00:18,223
Court, the last time
we saw each other,

871
01:00:18,258 --> 01:00:20,976
we were both running around
in our diapers.

872
01:00:21,011 --> 01:00:23,410
I'll bet that
was a sight.

873
01:00:23,445 --> 01:00:26,481
Mama says I used
to beat you up regularly

874
01:00:26,516 --> 01:00:27,948
with my sand pail.

875
01:00:27,983 --> 01:00:29,985
I wouldn't
try that these days.

876
01:00:32,988 --> 01:00:35,956
Everybody dig in.

877
01:00:35,991 --> 01:00:39,494
I, uh, imagine that you
work up quite an appetite

878
01:00:39,529 --> 01:00:42,497
handling the farm
all by yourself like that.

879
01:00:42,532 --> 01:00:44,464
It's a lot of work.

880
01:00:44,499 --> 01:00:47,002
I can't imagine
having the guts

881
01:00:47,037 --> 01:00:49,469
to tackle a job
that big.

882
01:00:49,504 --> 01:00:50,971
Yeah, well,
sometimes I wonder

883
01:00:51,006 --> 01:00:54,009
if I've bitten off
more than I can chew.

884
01:00:54,044 --> 01:00:56,511
I bet you'll
do just fine.

885
01:01:00,515 --> 01:01:02,017
Are you ok?

886
01:01:02,052 --> 01:01:02,983
Sure.

887
01:01:03,018 --> 01:01:04,519
I'm just fine.

888
01:01:09,524 --> 01:01:11,026
Well, thanks for dinner.

889
01:01:11,061 --> 01:01:11,992
You're welcome.

890
01:01:12,027 --> 01:01:14,529
