to apologize

1023
01:11:50,330 --> 01:11:52,832
for the last time
I saw you.

1024
01:11:53,333 --> 01:11:55,835
I was being unreasonable.

1025
01:11:57,837 --> 01:11:59,304
But when two people

1026
01:11:59,339 --> 01:12:00,840
really care about
each other...

1027
01:12:05,345 --> 01:12:08,348
well, when two people
really care...

1028
01:12:08,848 --> 01:12:10,350
they try
to understand things,

1029
01:12:10,850 --> 01:12:12,852
even when it's hard.

1030
01:12:14,854 --> 01:12:16,356
Don't you think so?

1031
01:12:20,360 --> 01:12:21,361
Yeah.

1032
01:12:22,362 --> 01:12:23,863
Sure.

1033
01:12:38,878 --> 01:12:40,880
Well, I'll
see you, ok?

1034
01:12:45,385 --> 01:12:46,386
Yeah.

1035
01:13:18,918 --> 01:13:22,422
I never thought
I could feel this way.

1036
01:13:23,923 --> 01:13:25,390
It's like,

1037
01:13:25,425 --> 01:13:26,891
I've been waiting

1038
01:13:26,926 --> 01:13:30,930
for you to come back
and find me, and...

1039
01:13:30,965 --> 01:13:33,933
now I'm afraid
it'll all go away.

1040
01:13:38,438 --> 01:13:40,440
I'm not going
anywhere.

1041
01:14:18,109 --> 01:14:19,611
Come on, Dani.

1042
01:14:21,112 --> 01:14:24,115
Unlock...
door.

1043
01:14:26,117 --> 01:14:27,584
He's unlocking it.

1044
01:14:27,619 --> 01:14:29,621
Daddy's going
to open it.

1045
01:14:30,622 --> 01:14:32,088
Come on, missy.

1046
01:14:32,123 --> 01:14:35,126
Let's put the baby to bed.

1047
01:14:36,127 --> 01:14:37,128
Maureen!

1048
01:14:42,634 --> 01:14:43,635
Maureen!

1049
01:14:49,140 --> 01:14:51,142
Where could she
have gotten off to?

1050
01:14:51,643 --> 01:14:54,646
She knew we'd be back
about noon.

1051
01:15:35,687 --> 01:15:37,654
I love you.

1052
01:15:37,689 --> 01:15:39,190
I love you, too.

1053
01:15:40,191 --> 01:15:41,693
I have to go.

1054
01:16:01,713 --> 01:16:03,464
What are we
going to do?

1055
01:16:03,499 --> 01:16:05,358
Don't think
about that.

1056
01:16:05,393 --> 01:16:07,306
We have to think
about it.

1057
01:16:07,341 --> 01:16:09,532
Not yet
we don't have to.

1058
01:16:09,567 --> 01:16:11,723
Yes, we do.
I have to go.

1059
01:16:11,758 --> 01:16:13,242
I'll see you later.

1060
01:16:13,277 --> 01:16:14,726
Court, come on.

1061
01:16:14,761 --> 01:16:15,692
Stop it.

1062
01:16:15,727 --> 01:16:17,729
You're going
to make me late.

1063
01:16:51,763 --> 01:16:54,766
Dani, I need
to talk to you.

1064
01:16:54,801 --> 01:16:55,767
Maureen!

1065
01:16:58,770 --> 01:17:01,272
Maureen, can you
get in here, please?

1066
01:17:04,776 --> 01:17:06,527
Where have you been?

1067
01:17:06,562 --> 01:17:08,279
The baby's home.

1068
01:18:37,368 --> 01:18:38,835
All right, boys.

1069
01:18:38,870 --> 01:18:41,372
Got to take
your brother his lunch.

1070
01:18:41,407 --> 01:18:42,839
He forgot it again.

1071
01:18:42,874 --> 01:18:45,626
Boy can't remember
his name these days.

1072
01:18:45,661 --> 01:18:48,379
I want you to sit there,
eat your lunch,

1073
01:18:48,414 --> 01:18:50,882
and no messing around,
you hear me?

1074
01:18:50,917 --> 01:18:52,401
Do you hear me?

1075
01:18:52,436 --> 01:18:53,885
Yes, ma'am.

1076
01:19:30,922 --> 01:19:31,923
Court?

1077
01:19:33,925 --> 01:19:34,875
Court!

1078
01:19:35,927 --> 01:19:36,928
Court!

1079
01:20:02,954 --> 01:20:04,455
Baby boy.

1080
01:20:10,461 --> 01:20:11,963
Court?

1081
01:20:14,465 --> 01:20:16,467
Go away, Dani.

1082
01:20:16,502 --> 01:20:18,469
Go away, Dani!

1083
01:20:18,504 --> 01:20:19,971
Go away!

1084
01:20:36,988 --> 01:20:38,739
Daddy!

1085
01:20:38,774 --> 01:20:40,133
Dani?

1086
01:20:40,168 --> 01:20:41,492
Daddy!

1087
01:20:42,994 --> 01:20:44,495
Daddy!

1088
01:20:44,996 --> 01:20:45,446
Daddy!

1089
01:20:45,997 --> 01:20:47,999
Dani, what's
the matter?

1090
01:20:48,034 --> 01:20:49,500
What's the matter?

1091
01:20:49,535 --> 01:20:50,501
It's Court.

1092
01:20:50,536 --> 01:20:51,467
What?

1093
01:20:51,502 --> 01:20:52,503
The tractor...

1094
01:20:52,538 --> 01:20:53,504
it's Court.

1095
01:20:53,539 --> 01:20:55,506
Help!

1096
01:21:00,511 --> 01:21:02,013
Abby!

1097
01:21:03,014 --> 01:21:04,515
Abby!

1098
01:22:41,027 --> 01:22:42,279
